  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK829">
<l>mikacceytu tammeḷḷu vārai nakacceytu </l>
<l>naṭpiṉuṭ cāppullaṟ pāṟṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It is the duty of kings to affect great love but make it die (inwardly) as regard those foes who shew them great friendship but despise them (in their heart).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
